Explore Our Fuel Cell Power Products 





                Heavy Duty Modules
            
From 30 kW to 200 kW net power, the modular FCveloCity® platform provides a flexible solution for your motive applications including forklifts, buses and light rail.
Learn more








                Fuel Cell Stacks
            
Ballard provides FCgen® and FCvelocity® fuel cell stacks to original equipment manufacturers and system integrators to power fuel cell systems.
Learn more








                Backup Power Systems
            
Ballard’s FCgen®-H2PM fuel cell system has been designed to integrate easily with existing power equipment.
Learn more



















