			Company Description 


			Ballard Power Systems, Inc. engages in design, development, manufacture, sale and service of fuel cell products. It provides clean energy fuel cell products enabling optimized power systems for a range of applications. The company operates through Fuel Cell Products and Services. The Fuel Cell Produ...
		


                Ballard Power Systems, Inc. engages in design, development, manufacture, sale and service of fuel cell products. It provides clean energy fuel cell products enabling optimized power systems for a range of applications. The company operates through Fuel Cell Products and Services. The Fuel Cell Products and Services segment consists of the sale, service and license of fuel cell products for telecom backup power and material handling and bus and distributed generation. Ballard Power Systems was founded on November 12, 2008 and is headquartered in Burnaby, Canada.
            




