Ballard has:

access to 2,000 patents/applications
over 250 MW of fuel cell products shipped
2.4 million MEAs manufactured
3,000 stationary systems delivered
more than 9 million kilometers in revenue service by fuel cell buses
$80 million contract with VW/Audi

